.SH NAME
\f[B]bookmark\-dlp\f[R] \- Program for downloading bookmarked YouTube
videos.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\ \ \ \f[CR]$ bookmark\-dlp \-\-source SOURCE \-\-target TARGET [OPTIONS]\f[R]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Utility program for downloading bookmarked YouTube links.
A program to replicate the folder structure of your
Chrome/Brave/Firefox/etc.
bookmarks and download all YouTube videos/playlists amongst the
bookmarks.
